description:
This is a recoded version of the 2 Ringside DVD's in muzzle1587's rip.

The original files are in Matroska .mkv format, which is unfortunately not very common. I have recoded them to DVD format using Magic Videoconverter version 8 (thanks to vrolok!) and Nero.
To my eyes, the overall quality of the endresult is rather good.

This has resulted in quite a large upload, but you can burn these 2 straight to DVD to enjoy on your Home Cinema System (or your TV as I like to call it ;)

So, if you are a not a techie but you are a Mike Tyson fan, grab these two, burn them as PAL-DVD and enjoy 6 hours of Mike's famous bouts!

BTW: my maximum upspeed is 50kb/s, so although I will seed 24/7 some patience is required!

Greetings to ya' all from The Breezin Dutchman!

